🧑‍💻 Personal 3D Portfolio Website
A visually captivating, fully responsive personal portfolio built using HTML, CSS, and JavaScript, featuring a custom 3D model embedded using Three.js. Designed to showcase projects, skills, and contact information in a seamless, interactive user experience.

🌐 Live Demo
🔗 View Website
(Add your deployed site URL here once live)

🚀 Features
🎨 Sleek, responsive design for desktop and mobile

🧩 3D model integration via Three.js or Spline

🧑‍💼 About section with tabbed skills interface

🛠️ Dynamic project showcase with hover effects

📬 Contact form with input styling and validation

🌙 Dark-themed UI with vibrant highlight accents

📱 Mobile menu toggle with icon-based navigation

